<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Verify your email address</h2>

  <p>Hi <%= @manager.email_address %>,</p>

  <p>Thank you for signing up for CrewControl! Please verify your email address to complete your registration and start managing your teams.</p>

  <p>
    <%= link_to "Verify Email Address", @verification_url, style: "display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;" %>
  </p>

  <p>Or copy and paste this link if the button above doesn't work:</p>
  <p><code><%= @verification_url %></code></p>

  <p>This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>

  <p>If you didn't create this account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

  <p>— The CrewControl Team</p>
</body>
</html>
